# Testing

## HOOK-ENFORCED (warned)
- Every new component and function MUST have tests. When writing a new `.tsx` component, a corresponding `.test.tsx` file should exist.

## INSTRUCTION RULES
- Vitest for unit and integration tests. Playwright for E2E tests.
- Tests MUST be co-located with source code: `Foo.test.tsx` lives next to `Foo.tsx`, not in a separate `__tests__/` directory.
- Follow existing test patterns in the project. Read existing tests before writing new ones.
